        spgc --full-output \
             --species-free-thresh {params.species_free_thresh} \
             --depth-ratio-thresh {params.depth_ratio_thresh} \
             --correlation-thresh {params.corr_thresh} \
             {input.depth} \
             {input.species_genes} \
             {input.partition} \
             {output}
        """


